<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>БЕЛ 8 клас – Интерактивен преговор</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=Source+Serif+4:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0f0e0c;
    --surface: #1a1814;
    --card: #201e1a;
    --border: #2e2b25;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-dim: #7a6330;
    --cream: #e8dfc8;
    --muted: #7a7060;
    --accent-blue: #4a8fa8;
    --accent-green: #5a8c6a;
    --accent-red: #a84a4a;
    --accent-purple: #7a5aa8;
    --text: #d4c9b0;
    --text-dim: #8a7d68;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3.5rem 1rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #c9a84c18 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .header-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
  .header-sub {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 1.5rem auto;
  }

  /* ── NAV TABS ── */
  .nav-wrap {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(15, 14, 12, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  .nav-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .nav-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .nav-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover { color: var(--cream); }
  .nav-btn.active {
    color: var(--gold);
    border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.35s ease; }
  .section.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── TOPIC CARDS ── */
  .topic-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .topic-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .topic-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-dim);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .topic-card-header {
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem 0.8rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .topic-icon {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .topic-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .topic-body {
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    display: none;
  }
  .topic-card.open .topic-body { display: block; }
  .topic-card.open { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .topic-card.open .topic-card-header { border-color: var(--gold-dim); }

  /* Accent colors per section */
  .lit-card .topic-card-header { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-blue); }
  .lang-card .topic-card-header { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-green); }
  .terms-card .topic-card-header { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-purple); }

  /* ── DEFINITION LIST ── */
  .def-list { list-style: none; }
  .def-item {
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.83rem;
  }
  .def-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .def-term {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .def-desc { color: var(--text); margin-top: 0.15rem; }

  /* ── WORKS TABLE ── */
  .works-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .works-table th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
  }
  .works-table td {
    padding: 0.65rem 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .works-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04); }
  .era-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .era-ant { background: rgba(74,143,168,0.2); color: var(--accent-blue); }
  .era-mid { background: rgba(168,74,74,0.2); color: #c07070; }
  .era-ren { background: rgba(90,140,106,0.2); color: var(--accent-green); }

  /* ── QUIZ ── */
  .quiz-wrap { max-width: 640px; }
  .quiz-progress-bar {
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 99px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .quiz-progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-dim), var(--gold));
    border-radius: 99px;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }
  .quiz-q-num {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .quiz-question {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .quiz-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .quiz-opt {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.1rem;
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .quiz-opt:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--gold-dim); color: var(--cream); }
  .quiz-opt.correct { background: rgba(90,140,106,0.15); border-color: var(--accent-green); color: #8fc89f; }
  .quiz-opt.wrong { background: rgba(168,74,74,0.15); border-color: var(--accent-red); color: #c07070; }
  .quiz-opt:disabled { cursor: default; }
  .quiz-feedback {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    display: none;
  }
  .quiz-feedback.show { display: block; }
  .quiz-feedback.ok { background: rgba(90,140,106,0.12); color: #8fc89f; border: 1px solid rgba(90,140,106,0.3); }
  .quiz-feedback.fail { background: rgba(168,74,74,0.12); color: #c07070; border: 1px solid rgba(168,74,74,0.3); }
  .quiz-next-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: none;
  }
  .quiz-next-btn.show { display: inline-block; }
  .quiz-next-btn:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .quiz-score-wrap {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    display: none;
  }
  .quiz-score-wrap.show { display: block; }
  .quiz-score-big {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .quiz-score-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .quiz-restart-btn {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gold);
    border: none;
    color: var(--bg);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  /* ── FLASHCARDS ── */
  .flashcard-wrap { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; perspective: 1200px; }
  .flashcard {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 220px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .flashcard.flipped { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .fc-face {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .fc-front {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .fc-back {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a14, #1e1c10);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }
  .fc-hint { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .fc-term {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .fc-def { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; }
  .fc-controls { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
  .fc-btn {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .fc-btn:hover { border-color: var(--gold-dim); color: var(--cream); }
  .fc-counter { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); min-width: 60px; text-align: center; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .topic-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .works-table { font-size: 0.76rem; }
    .works-table th, .works-table td { padding: 0.5rem 0.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-label">Министерство на образованието и науката</div>
  <h1>БЕЛ — <span>8. клас</span></h1>
  <p class="header-sub">Интерактивен преговор · Литература &amp; Български език</p>
  <div class="divider"></div>
</header>

<div class="nav-wrap">
  <div class="nav-tabs">
    <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showSection('lit')">📜 Литература</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('lang')">🔤 Езикознание</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('terms')">📖 Термини</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('quiz')">✏️ Тест</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('flash')">🃏 Флашкарти</button>
  </div>
</div>

<main>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       РАЗДЕЛ 1 – ЛИТЕРАТУРА
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div id="lit" class="section active">
    <h2 class="section-title">Литература</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Три културни епохи: Античност · Средновековие · Ренесанс. Кликни върху творба за подробности.</p>

    <!-- ВСИЧКИ ТВОРБИ – обзорна таблица -->
    <table class="works-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Творба</th><th>Автор</th><th>Жанр</th><th>Епоха</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Митове за Прометей, Едип; Троянски цикъл</td><td>Старогръцка митология</td><td>Митология</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ant">Античност</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Илиада" (I, VI, XXII, XXIV песен)</td><td>Омир</td><td>Епос</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ant">Античност</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Любов"</td><td>Сафо</td><td>Лирика</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ant">Античност</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Антигона"</td><td>Софокъл</td><td>Трагедия</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ant">Античност</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Библия (Битие, Евангелие от Матей и Йоан)</td><td>—</td><td>Религиозен текст</td><td><span class="era-badge era-mid">Средновековие</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Пространно житие на Константин–Кирил"</td><td>Климент Охридски</td><td>Житие / Агиография</td><td><span class="era-badge era-mid">Средновековие</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Азбучна молитва"</td><td>Константин Преславски</td><td>Акростих / Молитва</td><td><span class="era-badge era-mid">Средновековие</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„За буквите"</td><td>Черноризец Храбър</td><td>Полемично слово / Апология</td><td><span class="era-badge era-mid">Средновековие</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Притчата за трите пръстена" (Декамерон)</td><td>Джовани Бокачо</td><td>Новела</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ren">Ренесанс</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Дон Кихот" (I и VIII глава)</td><td>Мигел де Сервантес</td><td>Роман / Пародия</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ren">Ренесанс</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>„Хамлет"</td><td>Уилям Шекспир</td><td>Трагедия</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ren">Ренесанс</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Сонет 91 и Сонет 130</td><td>Уилям Шекспир</td><td>Сонет</td><td><span class="era-badge era-ren">Ренесанс</span></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- КАРТИ ПО ЕПОХИ -->
    <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;color:var(--accent-blue);font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;">⚡ АНТИЧНОСТ</h3>
    <div class="topic-grid" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">

      <div class="topic-card lit-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="topic-card-header"><span class="topic-icon">⚔️</span><span class="topic-title">Митове (Прометей, Едип, Троянски цикъл)</span></div>
        <div class="topic-body">
          <ul class="def-list">
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Прометей</span><span class="def-desc"> – открадва огъня от боговете и го дава на хората; наказан – прикован към скала.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Едип</span><span class="def-desc"> – убива баща си и се жени за майка си, без да знае; символ на слепотата на човека спрямо съдбата.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Троянски цикъл</span><span class="def-desc"> – митове около Троянската война: Парис, Елена, 10-годишната обсада, Ахилес, Хектор.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Митология</span><span class="def-desc"> – съвкупност от митове на даден народ.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Митологичен цикъл</span><span class="def-desc"> – група митове с общи герои и теми.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="topic-card lit-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="topic-card-header"><span class="topic-icon">🏛️</span><span class="topic-title">„Илиада" – Омир</span></div>
        <div class="topic-body">
          <ul class="def-list">
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Жанр</span><span class="def-desc"> – героичен епос; изучават се I (гнявът на Ахил), VI (Хектор и Андромаха), XXII (смъртта на Хектор), XXIV (изкуплението).</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Главен конфликт</span><span class="def-desc"> – гневът на Ахил срещу Агамемнон → смъртта на Патрокъл → отмъщение → помирение с Приам.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Постоянен епитет</span><span class="def-desc"> – устойчив израз, свързан с герой: „бързоногият Ахил", „розовопръстата зора".</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Епическо сравнение</span><span class="def-desc"> – разгърнато сравнение, което само по себе си рисува картина: „като лъв, що нападнал стадо..."</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="topic-card lit-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="topic-card-header"><span class="topic-icon">💛</span><span class="topic-title">„Любов" – Сафо</span></div>
        <div class="topic-body">
          <ul class="def-list">
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Жанр</span><span class="def-desc"> – лирика; стихотворение за физическото и емоционалното въздействие на любовта.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Тема</span><span class="def-desc"> – ревността и страстта; субективното преживяване е изразено чрез телесни симптоми (треска, шум в ушите).</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Лирика</span><span class="def-desc"> – литературен род, в центъра е чувството на лирическия аз.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="topic-card lit-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="topic-card-header"><span class="topic-icon">🎭</span><span class="topic-title">„Антигона" – Софокъл</span></div>
        <div class="topic-body">
          <ul class="def-list">
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Жанр</span><span class="def-desc"> – трагедия.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Конфликт</span><span class="def-desc"> – Антигона иска да погребе брат си Полиник (Божи закон) ↔ Креон забранява (държавен закон).</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Трагически герой</span><span class="def-desc"> – благороден герой с фатален недостатък, унищожен от собствения си избор.</span></li>
            <li class="def-item"><span class="def-term">Катарзис</span><span class="def-desc"> – очистване на зрителя от страх и съжаление чрез трагедията.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

